   "source": [
    "# Geometric Sequence\n",
    "\n",
    "any [sequence](sequence.ipynb) in the form of:\n",
    "$$ a, ar,ar^2,...,ar^n; r\\neq1 $$ "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d338c15f-6052-405f-8dd6-f3f97593ac4f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "And the geometric sum is:\n",
    "$$ a+ar+ar^2+...+ar^n = a\\frac{1-r^{n+1}}{1-r}; r\\neq1 $$ "
   ]
  }
 ],
